  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK830">
<l>pakainaṭpāṅ kālam varuṅkāṉ mukanaṭ </l>
<l>ṭakanaṭ porīi viṭal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When one's foes begin to affect friendship, one should love them with one's looks, and, cherishing no love in the heart, give up (even the former).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
